text: Philipsburg is the capital city of Sint Maarten. In 2017, 1,894 people lived there. Philipsburg was founded in 1763 by John Philips, a Scottish captain in the Dutch navy. == References == Category:1763 establishments Category:1760s establishments in North America Category:Capital cities in North America Category:Sint Maarten
title: Philipsburg, Sint Maarten
